Package: ARF
Title: ARF - R package for the Analysis of rRNA Fragments originating from Ribo-seq experiments
Version: 1.0.1
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Ferhat",
           family = "Alkan",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
